<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Account Locked</title>
  </head>
  <body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333">
    <div
      style="
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
        border: 1px solid #ddd;
        border-radius: 5px;
      "
    >
      <h2 style="color: #d9534f">Account Locked</h2>
      <p>Hello <%= name %>,</p>
      <p>
        We are writing to inform you that your account on EV-Market has been
        locked by an administrator.
      </p>
      <p><strong>Reason:</strong> <%= reason %></p>
      <p>
        If you believe this is a mistake or wish to appeal this decision, please
        contact our support team at
        <a href="mailto:<%= supportEmail %>"><%= supportEmail %></a>.
      </p>
      <p>Thank you for your understanding.</p>
      <p>Best regards,<br />The EV-Market Team</p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
